Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:56.19,white-large,,0,0,0,,{\pos(393,295)}The Magic Marker Cap
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:59.39,white-large,,0,0,0,,Not enough to tell anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:02.09,white-large,,0,0,0,,small as a sesame seed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:06.43,white-large,,0,0,0,,Today's discovery
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:09.93,white-large,,0,0,0,,When I put on a magic marker cap
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:12.97,white-large,,0,0,0,,it makes a click
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:16.44,white-large,,0,0,0,,what's that click?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:19.84,white-large,,0,0,0,,looking at the cap
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:23.62,white-large,,0,0,0,,there are these little bumps
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:25.78,white-large,,0,0,0,,hidden stoppers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:30.29,white-large,,0,0,0,,This is the source of the click.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:33.12,white-large,,0,0,0,,it's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:37.36,white-large,,0,0,0,,Today's discovery
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:43.97,white-large,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow there will probably be another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:47.64,black-large,,0,0,0,,{\pos(387,37)}one each day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:47.64,black-large,,0,0,0,,{\pos(464,141)}today's discovery
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:58.28,black-small,,0,0,0,,{\pos(207,117)}Q: What will happen when we raise the iron ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the answer from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, did you think carefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's do it for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer it number 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The two iron balls stay together
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, if we try to raise the iron balls a bit higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you suppose will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it fell. Let's try that once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As we saw, it falls.\NWhy do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When iron is brought near a magnet, instantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on we think for ourselves.
